            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info">
        <div class="name"><span class="info_label">Name:</span><br />Swing Trade Portfolio</div><!-- 
     --><div class="updated"><span class="info_label">Updated:</span><br />12/29/2021</div>
